      "comment": "NANGAR FLY (7) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (25.10) at this track over 431m. Will break from a wide draw. Can measure up again. SHORTY (3) has a strong record here with three wins and three placings from nine starts. Below best last time at this track (25.62) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length seventh. Looks a key chance on best figures. MY FAIRY BREAD (2) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (30.29) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Gosford. Can improve sharply here. SWIFT ELI (1) has strong credentials from this draw.",
